    <string name="terms">Terms &amp; Conditions</string>
    <string name="terms_details">Welcome to Markly!\n\nBy using this app, you agree to the following terms:\n\n1. Data Storage\nYour bookmarks are stored locally on your device. We do not collect or share your personal data.\n\n2. Export and Import\nYou can export your bookmarks to a JSON file and import them back. These files are stored in your device\'s Downloads folder.\n\n3. User Responsibility\nYou are responsible for the URLs and content you bookmark. Please ensure you have the right to access the websites you save.\n\n4. App Usage\nThis app is provided as-is for educational purposes. We are not responsible for any data loss.\n\n5. Privacy\nMarkly respects your privacy. All data remains on your device and is never uploaded to any server.\n\n6. Updates\nWe may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the app means you accept any changes.\n\nThank you for using Markly!</string>
